div3.p:
Every thing
                        about as usual in camp The Sailors came in to day We get no potatoes to day I make meal
                        Slapjacks for supper and bake a loaf of corn Dodger{4}

Nothing comes in to day that we can speculate on. one of the boys at the bakery sends in
some ginger Cakes and onions. No rumors to day. We hear that the off-icers are to be
taken out of the Stockade and sent to Charleston for Exchange {5}
